title: The Best Of ZZ Top (1977)        FLAC        ak6103
description: The Best Of ZZ Top (1977)        FLAC What we got some ZZ to pass time to What is real good about this release is it is the ZZ Before Eliminator this is the bluesy Texas ZZ of the 70's Not sayin that there's anything wrong with the 80's ZZ Its just not the same but thats what I think and Im not claimin perfect not by a longshot..........Enjoy and seed if ya keep it
